Your dream's about to come true.

12:22.059 --> 12:23.925
Should we hug?
I feel like maybe we should hug.

12:24.027 --> 12:26.461
Okay, quick one... with back taps.

12:30.367 --> 12:31.266
Oh, my God!

12:31.368 --> 12:32.601
