Greetings, mortals!

17:08.627 --> 17:10.194
He told me he wasn't gonna do this.

17:10.296 --> 17:16.634
Prepare to be transported
to a magical land of wonder...

17:16.736 --> 17:18.670
and illusion.

17:21.441 --> 17:22.440
Loser!

17:23.609 --> 17:25.510
Now I need a volunteer.

17:25.612 --> 17:26.944
What about you?

17:27.047 --> 17:28.780
Come on. Don't be shy.

17:28.882 --> 17:30.381
Let's give her some encouragement, yeah?

17:30.426 --> 17:31.254
Yeah.

17:35.255 --> 17:37.889
Yes, very nice.
Big round of applause for, um...

17:37.991 --> 17:39.057
Sorry. What's your name?

17:39.159 --> 17:42.026
- Chloe.
- Chloe, everyone!

17:42.128 --> 17:43.394
Chloe!

17:43.496 --> 17:44.662
We're gonna have to move.

17:44.764 --> 17:47.331
All right, now, in you go, Chloe.

17:47.434 --> 17:49.033
All right. Perfect.

17:49.135 --> 17:50.301
You comfy?

17:51.938 --> 17:55.373
And now comes the fun part...

17:55.475 --> 17:59.177
real... steel... swords!

17:59.279 --> 18:00.545
Where the hell did he get swords?

18:00.647 --> 18:01.546
I have no idea.

18:01.648 --> 18:03.414
And now, dear Chloe,

18:03.516 --> 18:08.820
I am about to transport you
to a land of wonder.

18:08.922 --> 18:10.388
Oh, my God!

18:10.490 --> 18:12.356
Uh, uh, wha... No, no, no, no, no!

18:12.459 --> 18:13.991
No, no, no, Chloe! I'm so sorry, Chloe!

18:14.094 --> 18:16.327
No, no, no, no, no, no, no! Uh, uh...

18:16.429 --> 18:18.763
Chloe?! Chloe?!

18:21.201 --> 18:23.501
Well, that's strange.

18:23.603 --> 18:25.536
- Oh, my God!
- Oh...

18:25.638 --> 18:27.772
Chloe?

18:28.942 --> 18:30.341
Yeah!

18:30.433 --> 18:31.342
Whoo!

18:31.444 --> 18:33.143
That was amazing!

