Yeah! That's my son!

18:36.950 --> 18:39.517
That's my son!

18:39.619 --> 18:41.919
- Dude, that was awesome!
- Ben, that was incredible!

18:42.021 --> 18:43.221
- Oh, my God!
- Thank you.

18:43.323 --> 18:45.223
- That was so amazing!
- Thanks.

18:45.325 --> 18:47.058
I thought you said you were
gonna go a different way.

18:47.160 --> 18:48.226
I did.

18:48.328 --> 18:50.461
Until today, Chloe was my assistant.

18:50.563 --> 18:52.029
When you said, "Fly under the radar,"

18:52.132 --> 18:53.598
I figured you meant
plant her in the audience

18:53.700 --> 18:54.932
as a reluctant volunteer.

18:56.035 --> 18:57.635
That's <i> exactly</i> what I meant.

18:57.737 --> 19:00.404
You nailed it. You nailed it.

19:00.507 --> 19:02.573
You know, I-I saw some kids
give some mean looks,

19:02.675 --> 19:04.108
but you just kept going.

19:04.210 --> 19:05.309
That was so brave, Ben.

19:05.411 --> 19:06.911
People who think magic is lame

19:07.013 --> 19:08.946
just haven't seen
the right person do it yet.

19:09.048 --> 19:11.215
I know how to make magic cool.

19:11.317 --> 19:12.450
It's like you.

19:12.552 --> 19:14.986
- <i>Nobody</i> thinks radio is cool...
- Mm...

19:15.088 --> 19:18.156
...but when <i> you</i> do it, it's amazing.

19:21.227 --> 19:22.660
What? What did I say?

19:22.762 --> 19:25.096
Exactly what I needed to hear.

19:25.198 --> 19:27.632
Everybody... in the van!

