- Mr. Sacca, wait!
- Schuman?

19:46.619 --> 19:47.985
How the hell did you get out here?

19:48.087 --> 19:49.954
I... may have driven through
a security gate,

19:50.056 --> 19:51.689
but I had to tell you something.

19:51.791 --> 19:54.859
You asked me earlier... what's
my company's unfair advantage?

19:54.961 --> 19:56.527
Well, it's me.

19:56.629 --> 19:58.362
What I do is really, really hard,

19:58.464 --> 20:00.198
and no one does it better than I do.

20:00.300 --> 20:02.166
So if you don't want in, that's fine.

20:02.268 --> 20:03.801
I will find someone who does,

20:03.903 --> 20:07.638
and I will make them very, very rich.

20:07.740 --> 20:09.440
Much richer than this.

20:11.044 --> 20:12.443
All right!

20:12.545 --> 20:14.478
That's what I've been
looking for from you, man!

20:14.581 --> 20:15.713
Some fire!

20:15.815 --> 20:17.448
I mean, driving up here like this,

20:17.550 --> 20:19.383
- busting through that gate...
- I know!

20:19.485 --> 20:22.119
...which those guys are
definitely gonna arrest you for.

20:23.590 --> 20:24.655
That's passion.

20:24.757 --> 20:26.390
That's what it takes to build a company.

20:26.492 --> 20:29.093
But before I go all-in,
I still got to know,

20:29.195 --> 20:30.494
what's the first show about?

20:30.597 --> 20:34.665
<i>Okay, it was time to shine,
but my mind went blank.</i>

20:34.767 --> 20:36.400
It should be this.

20:38.471 --> 20:40.171
Yes! Yes! This is the show.

20:40.273 --> 20:41.706
This is the first show.

20:41.808 --> 20:45.142
It... It... It's a show
about a-a guy like me

20:45.245 --> 20:47.211
with a family like them.

20:47.313 --> 20:50.047
Yeah, a guy who has no business
starting his own business,

20:50.149 --> 20:52.350
but he's going for it anyway.

20:52.452 --> 20:54.085
And he'll make lots of mistakes.

20:54.187 --> 20:55.186
He'll lie to his wife.

20:55.288 --> 20:56.888
Only once.

20:56.990 --> 20:58.389
And she'll forgive him?

20:59.525 --> 21:00.558
Eventually.

21:00.660 --> 21:01.592
Maybe.

21:04.197 --> 21:05.529
A-And we don't know how it'll turn out.

21:05.632 --> 21:08.032
I mean, he could succeed, he could fail,

21:08.134 --> 21:10.001
but either way, I promise you,

21:10.103 --> 21:13.237
