21:13.339 --> 21:14.505
I love it.

21:14.607 --> 21:16.607
It's the American dream.

21:16.709 --> 21:17.942
I'm in.

21:18.044 --> 21:20.244
Yes! What did I tell you?!

21:23.116 --> 21:24.682
Thank you, Mr. Sacca!

